<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Not Found - MUBAS Grading System</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .error-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            color: #1e3c72;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <div class="error-title">Page Not Found</div>
        <p>The page you are looking for doesn't exist or has been moved.</p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>